HEADWORD: Spenserian
<hw>Spen*se"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to the English poet <ets>Spenser</ets>; -- specifically applied to the
stanza used in his poem ⟦ldquo⟧The Fa⟦eum⟧rie Queene.⟦rdquo⟧</def>⟦br⟧
